# Freeze Violation — WITHOUT Sponsio (breach trajectory)
Output assets/demos/freeze_violation_without.gif

Env PYTHONPATH "."

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set Padding 20
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 20ms

Type "sponsio demo --scenario freeze --no-guard"
Enter
Sleep 10s
Sleep 3s
